== Definition ==

<b>mouse</b> (<i>noun</i>), plural <b>mice</b> [1]
# A small [[rodent]].
# (<i>computers</i>) A [[pointing device]] to be used with a [[graphical display]]. (compare [[joystick]], [[trackpad]], [[laptop nipple]])

<b>mouse</b> (<i>verb</i>)
# (<i>naut.</i>) To close the mouth of a hook by a careful binding of [[marline]] or wire.

Ex.
:<i>Captain Higgins <b>moused</b> the hook with a bit of [[marline]] to prevent the [[block]] [[becket | beckets]] from falling out under slack</i>

== Pronunciation ==

<b>mouse</b>
